        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses concept of intelligence in his <hi rend="italic">Earthworms</hi> manuscript.</p> 
            <p>Remarks on GJR’s work on echinoderms.</p> 
<p>Comments on Wilhelm Roux [<hi rend="italic">Der Kampf der Theile im Organismus</hi> (1881)].</p> 
            <p>Discusses animal instincts, citing Fabre’s description of sand-wasps.</p>
        </abstract>
